WEBVTT

00:00.179 --> 00:03.600
Welcome to Westchester Medical Center's new hybrid operating room,...

00:03.943 --> 00:06.878
...a  state-of-the-art operating suite specifically designed...

00:06.975 --> 00:09.027
...for the use of catheter-based treatments.

00:09.765 --> 00:14.916
The new hybrid OR combines the best features of a modern operating room and a catheterization lab...

00:15.092 --> 00:17.481
...using the most sophisticated imaging technology...

00:17.566 --> 00:20.698
...and featuring the latest advances in surgical and imaging equipment,...

00:21.163 --> 00:25.061
...making it an ideal solution for performing complex, minimally invasive...

00:25.197 --> 00:30.175
...and open cardiovascular, vascular, neurovascular and orthopedic procedures...

00:30.244 --> 00:31.875
...in the same operating space.

